  "The decibel level of sound is L = 10 * ln(I/I_0)/ln(10), where I is intensity. If I = 0.001 watts/m^2 is increasing at 0.0001 watts/m^2 per second, what is dL/dt?": "L=10 * In(I_0)/ln(10),音频的分贝水平为10。如果I=0.001瓦特/平方米,每秒0.0001瓦特/平方米,什么是dL/dt?",
  "L = 10*log_10(I/I_0), so dL/dI = 10/(I * ln(10)). Then dL/dt = dL/dI * dI/dt = [10/(I * ln(10))] * 0.0001. At I = 0.001: dL/dt = 10/(0.001 * ln(10)) * 0.0001 = 1/ln(10) dB/s.": "L = 10*log_10(I/I_0), 所以dL/dI = 10/(I * In(10)), 然后dL/dt = dL/dI * dI/dt = [10/(I * In(10))] * 0.0001, at I = 0.001: dL/dt = 10/(0.001 * In(10)) * 0.0001 = 1/ln(10) dB/s。",
  "The Richter scale magnitude is M = (2/3)log_10(E/E_0). If the energy E of an earthquake is increasing at 10^12 joules/s and currently E = 10^15 joules, what is dM/dt? (Use E_0 = 1.)": "如果地震的能量E在10°12焦耳/秒上升,目前E=10°15焦耳,那么DM/dt是什么? (使用E_0=1)",
